BLAZE CAFE — <%= @event.to_s.humanize %>
Ref: <%= @order.reference %>

<% case @event
   when :order_received -%>
We got your order. We'll start prepping as soon as payment is confirmed.
<% when :order_paid -%>
Payment confirmed. Kitchen is on it.
<% when :order_ready -%>
<%= @order.delivery? ? "Your order is leaving the kitchen — driver on the way." : "Your order is ready — come through to the counter." %>
<% when :order_out_for_delivery -%>
Out for delivery. The driver will call when close.
<% when :order_delivered -%>
Delivered. Enjoy the fire.
<% end -%>

Items:
<% @order.order_items.each do |item| -%>
  <%= item.quantity %>× <%= item.name_snapshot %> — ₦<%= (item.subtotal_kobo / 100).to_s.reverse.scan(/\d{1,3}/).join(",").reverse %>
<% end -%>

Total: ₦<%= (@order.total_kobo / 100).to_s.reverse.scan(/\d{1,3}/).join(",").reverse %>
Fulfillment: <%= @order.fulfillment.humanize %>

Blaze Cafe · Ondo State
